title: Dj.Nece's Ladies Nightout 2
description:
Hellos once again this is my second Ladies Nightout mix I placed some really 
good songs just in case you missed them or did not hear them last year well they are here. I hope that you can pass the word on this mix I am here just for you and thank you for choosing my mixes for your players. An unsigned artist is not an artist without the support of you the listeners. Here is the play list:

Intro
Ronny Ringo and Jimmy having some fun with my nickname Clowns!
The Review of last mix
1.Timbaland Feat One Republic-Apologize(Peter Rauhofer Recopnstruction Mix)Awesome work Peter you are an inspiration
2.Wally Lopez Feat. Hadley VI- Burning Inside(Tikaro, J Louis and Ferran Remix VS Albert Neve Strings Remix) Dj.Nece's ProLong Mix
3.Wally Lopez-Shake It Like(David Amo & Julio Navas Remix) Mixed with Everything But The Girl-Missing
4.Cascade-Faded(Dave Ramone Electro Club Extended)
5.Ackcent-Lovers Cry(Extended Mix)
6.Lenny Fontana and Ridney Pres. larisa-Wait 4 You(Vodoo and Serano Remix)
7.Despreciados VS Waiter Master J-Ibiza(Club Mix)
8.Pitbull-I Know You Want Me(Calle Ocho More English Extended Mix)
9.The Doors-Light My Fire(Hot Rocks Club Remix)Old But Goodie
10.Guru Josh Project-Infinity 2008 (Klass Remix)
11.The Tamperer Feat.Maya-Feel It 2009(Pop Trumpet Club)Every mix to this track just simply rocks get them all!
12.Louie Lou Gorbea Feat.Miss Patty-R U Feeling Me(Tiger Stripes Remix)
13.Ernest Kohi- Say Adieu(The Paul Goodyear Big Room Club Mix)
14.Candy Williams Feat.Whiteside-Time Is Right(JOrge Martin S Dub Mix-Milk and sugar Edit)
15.Leonid Rudenko Feat.Danielle-Summerfish 2009(Wendel Kos First Sunlight Mix)
16.Sylvia Tosun and Loverush UK-5 Reasons(Original)
17.The Killers-Spaceman(Bimbo Jones Vocal)

AS you wanted and here it is ok Ladies Nightout was good for the ladies so enjoy ok tell a friend or all your friends and dont forget to give me feed back. Again Thank you very much for choosing me hugs to you all.
Love
Nece
